<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span style="color:#707070">[في الانكليزية]</span> Semantic change by a syntactic change of the same word<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
